snippet.title: No Stars, Only Constellations (game trailer) (formerly: "Polaris")
snippet.description:
No Stars, Only Constellations (formerly "Polaris") is a first person go-on-a-lousy-stargazing-date-and-then-get-dumped-at-the-end simulator. https://radiatoryang.itch.io/nostars

Game by Robert Yang et al

SITE: http://www.debacle.us/

MUSIC: Bark Hide and Horn -- Firefly
